notes=HDD FATX Fix.<br><br>1. Apply this JMP patch to default.xbe, overwrite the original file.<br>2. Download the 5 files: https://jayxbox.com/All-Patches/titles/TOCA%20Race%20Driver%203%20(DTM%20Race%20Driver%203)%20(Pro%20Race%20Driver%203)%20(V8%20Supercars%20Australia%203)/TOCA3_HDDFIX.zip <br>3. Place the 5 files into the game's main dir<br>4. Delete the original 5 files that were already there (their names are too long for the FATX filesystem and won't transfer over).
